cdata.name: Setcoin
cdata.desc: The Inserviss Platform is a Global Mobile Marketplace that connects service providers and customers. It allows service providers to join, publish their services, offer promotions and loyalty campaigns, and get feedback from consumers. For consumers it enables a convenient way to order and book custom services using a streamlined and secure mobile application. Setcoin is a token based on the Waves Platform. It's used for payments between Service Providers & Customers.
